description:
Nurture the sapling of higher consciousness & evolve as a blissful person with spirituo-scientific Preksha meditation techniques!!
Are you seeking calmness, peace of mind, joy, vibrant health, greater energy, positive relationships and fulfilment in life? Do you wish to be stress-free? Then Blossom with Preksha meditation & Transform your soul.
Lot of people like the idea of meditation but rarely get a chance to doing anything about it. That's why we have designed Preksha Meditation App . The sapling of consciousness is within You & now nurturing this is possible at your finger tips. Dive deep into yourself and enrich your life through Preksha meditation. Nullify the negative vibrations in the environment, creating a more harmonious environment. 
Preksha meditation is a simple meditation technique with its root in Jainism - a Jain meditation technique.However this app is for anyone with an interest in developing their physical, mental, emotional & spiritual wellbeing, it is not keen in pushing any particular belief system, religion or otherwise.
This captivating guided meditation app combines modern techniques and ancient principles. Even without prior experience, you can enjoy deep relaxation, stress relief and other benefits of meditation with our Apps.
Preksha dhyan is an Indian meditation technique which is practiced by more than 2.5 lac people worldwide 
Now available. Download.
Our Apps Feature:
 •Guided Meditation for beginners and amateurs to practice Meditation and    Relaxation. 
•Meditation Timer for practising meditation with intervals
•Blissful Reciters and Meditation music.
•Upcoming Meditation Camp Details
•Meditation Practice History Calendar to keep a record of daily practices
•Meditation tips on how to meditate and FAQs to answer your questions and queries
•Querying facility to solve your ideas or put forth your suggestions
•Details about the meditation technique, founder, Related Guide, benefits of meditation, Details of Preksha Meditation centers and much more.
